-- Cove Energy Drawing ‘Serious Interest,’ Standard Chartered Says
-- B y   E d u a r d   G i s m a t u l l i n
-- 2012-02-21T12:09:44Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-02-21/cove-energy-drawing-serious-interest-standard-chartered-says.html
Cove Energy Plc (COV) , the London-based
oil and gas explorer that’s put itself up for sale, is receiving
interest from national and international oil companies, Standard
Chartered Bank said.  “There is a lot of serious interest across the board,”
said  John Martin , a managing director at Standard Chartered,
which is advising Cove on the sale. “There are serious
contenders.”  Martin, who declined to name the potential bidders, said
both the world’s biggest listed oil companies and national oil
producers are interested.  To contact the reporter on this story:
